% ============================================================
% Section 9: Conclusion
% ============================================================
\section{Conclusion}

Al-Marjaa represents a significant advancement in making programming accessible to Arabic speakers. By providing a comprehensive, production-ready programming language with native Arabic syntax and integrated AI capabilities, it addresses a critical gap in the global programming landscape.

\textarabic{كأَوَّل لُغةِ بَرمَجةٍ عَرَبِيَّة تَجمَع بَين تِقنِيَّات التَّجميع الحَديثَة والقُدرات AI المُدمَجَة، لُغةُ المَرجِع لَها القُدرَة عَلى تَحفيز الاِبتِكار التِّقنيّ في العالَم العَرَبِيّ.}

\textbf{Key Results:}
\begin{itemize}
    \item 343 unit tests with 99.4\% pass rate
    \item 5.08x JIT speedup
    \item 19.9M operations/second peak performance
    \item 30+ Arabic-optimized UI components
\end{itemize}

